-- Control NPC LocalScript (underground + stable platform; velocity resetting + player platform)
-- Modified to: 1) ensure local player always remains under NPC surface even if NPC is very thin
--             2) make player platform follow the local player continuously, recreate after respawn
--             3) destroy platforms when toggle is turned off and recreate on toggle on (works after respawn)
-- Place this in StarterPlayer > StarterPlayerScripts

